fr.sii.ogham.core.util.bean

Class MapBeanReadWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sii.ogham.core.util.bean.MapBeanReadWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BeanReadWrapper, Map<String,Object>

    public class MapBeanReadWrapper
extends Object
implements BeanReadWrapper, Map<String,Object>
    Wraps a bean and exposes as a Map. The Map is indexed by the property names defined in the bean and allow to access the value using the Map insterface. This implementation doesn't support update methods (remove, clear, put...) and doesn't support access to values directly (values, containsValue). This implementation delegates access to real bean properties through a SimpleBeanReadWrapper instance (by default). You can override this default wrapper using the constructor MapBeanReadWrapper(BeanReadWrapper).
